  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mad Miner is a mining game where you try to survive in a new order where world life is trapped underground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to survive by taking care of your oxygen and hunger in procedurally generated mines!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458700/extras/634a3ed6355d4ee3ab3b0b5dd18b7476.poster.avif?t=1766583591\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458700/extras/634a3ed6355d4ee3ab3b0b5dd18b7476.webm?t=1766583591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458700/extras/634a3ed6355d4ee3ab3b0b5dd18b7476.mp4?t=1766583591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant and harvest crops, produce oxygen with the oxygen machine, and dig up everything that comes your way! Sit back and play comfortably. Pay attention to your oxygen level and hunger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458700/extras/b6dff0f03a6721304d2164dda575924d.avif?t=1766583591\" width=1172 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your own production benches to produce. Some welds can be produced in some special looms. Get materials to craft items and resources for materials too! You will not understand how time flies as you get lost in this beautiful cycle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mad Miner has an enjoyable resource gathering cycle. It is neither too complex nor too simple.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458700/extras/5dd83ad19c300007517a525d2eb70566.avif?t=1766583591\" width=1172 height=292 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mad Miner is a mining game where you try to survive in a new order where world life is trapped underground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to survive by taking care of your oxygen and hunger in procedurally generated mines!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458700/extras/634a3ed6355d4ee3ab3b0b5dd18b7476.poster.avif?t=1766583591\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458700/extras/634a3ed6355d4ee3ab3b0b5dd18b7476.webm?t=1766583591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458700/extras/634a3ed6355d4ee3ab3b0b5dd18b7476.mp4?t=1766583591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plant and harvest crops, produce oxygen with the oxygen machine, and dig up everything that comes your way! Sit back and play comfortably. Pay attention to your oxygen level and hunger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458700/extras/b6dff0f03a6721304d2164dda575924d.avif?t=1766583591\" width=1172 height=292 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your own production benches to produce. Some welds can be produced in some special looms. Get materials to craft items and resources for materials too! You will not understand how time flies as you get lost in this beautiful cycle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mad Miner has an enjoyable resource gathering cycle. It is neither too complex nor too simple.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2458700/extras/5dd83ad19c300007517a525d2eb70566.avif?t=1766583591\" width=1172 height=292 /></span></p>",
